[{"phelps":"AB10714","text":"O Gott, treck düsse Kinner ran. Düsse Kinner sünd Planten vun Dien Appelhoff, Blomen vun Dien Wisch, Rosen vun Dien Gaarn. Laat Dien Rägen up jüm fallen; laat de Wahrheitssünn up jüm mit Dien Leevde schienen. Laat Dien Bries' jüm upfrischen, dat se tolehrt wardt, groot wardt un sik entwickelt un in vullkamene Schöönheit vörtüüg' kaamt. Du büst de Schinker. Du büst de Barmhartige.","name":"Gebääd för Kinner","source":"bahaiprayers.org","version":"39507739-5499-4ef4-bde2-202fd1a6c146","translations":[{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"naq","lang_name":"Khoekhoegowab"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"med","lang_name":"Melpa"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"zh-Hans","lang_name":"Simplified Chinese"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"}]},{"phelps":"AB11094","text":"O mien Gott! O Du Vergäver vun Sünnen, Schinker vun Gaven, Verdriever vun Leedsaal!\n\nFörwahr, ik prans' Di an, dat Du de Sünnen vergäven wullst vun de, de dat eerdsche Kleed afleggt hebbt un na de geestliche Welt upstägen sünd.\n\nO mien Herr! Maak jüm rein vun jüm ähr Schuld, verdriev' jüm jüm ähr Dröövnis, un maak jüm ähr Düüsternis to Licht. Maak, dat se in d'n Gaarn vun't Glück rinkaamt, wasch jüm rein mit dat reinste Water, un laat to, dat se up d'n höögsten Barg Dien Pracht to sehn kriegt.","name":"Gebääd för de Afgestorven","source":"bahaiprayers.org","version":"bcb30585-9436-4f4d-969f-3eb1ac2755ef","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"hr","lang_name":"Croatian"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"gux","lang_name":"Gourmanchéma"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"ik","lang_name":"Inupiaq"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"naq","lang_name":"Khoekhoegowab"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"kgf","lang_name":"Kube"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mt","lang_name":"Maltese"},{"language":"mr","lang_name":"Marathi"},{"language":"mh","lang_name":"Marshallese"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"kj","lang_name":"Oshikwanyama"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"se","lang_name":"Sami"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"sl","lang_name":"Slovenian"},{"language":"st","lang_name":"Southern Sotho"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"ABU0137","text":"O Du goodhartige Herr! Du hest de hele Minschheit vun een un d'n sülven Stamm schapen. Du hest beschickt, dat all de Minschen to een un de sülve Familie höört. In Dien hillig Bisien sünd se all Dien Deners, un de hele Minschheit wardt ünner Dien Tabernakel bescheermt; se sünd an Dien Tafel vun de Œverflood tohoopkamen; se wardt all anlüchtt vun Dien Vœrsorg ähr Licht.\n\nO Gott! Du büst goodhartig to all de Minschen, sorgst vör elkeen, giffst elkeen Schuul, giffst elkeen Läven. Du hest all un elkeen begaavt un kumpabel maakt, hest jüm in de See vun Dien Gnaad' induukt.\n\nO Du goodhartige Herr! Verenig jüm alltohoop. Maak, dat de Religionen een Sinns wardt, un maak de Völker eens, dat se enanner as een Familie ankiekt un de Eerd' as een Huus. Möögt se all mit enanner in vullkamene Eendracht tosamenläven.\n\nO Gott! Hääv' hoog dat Banner vun all de Minschenkinner ähr Eenheit.\n\nO Gott! Bring us d'n Allergröttsten Vräden.\n\nSmääd' Du, o Gott, de Harten tosamen.\n\nO Du goodhartige Vadder, Gott! Hœg' use Harten mit d'n Röök vun Dien Leevde. Maak use Ogen hell mit dat Licht vun Dien Anledden. Bring use Ohren Hœg' mit de Melodie vun Dien Woord, un gääv' us alltohoop Schuul in de Hoogborg vun Dien Vörsicht.\n\nDu büst de Mächtige un Kräftige, Du büst de Vergävene un Du büst De, De de hele Minschheit ähr Fählers nich tellt.","name":"Vrädengebääd","source":"bahaiprayers.org","version":"fb7dbb6c-a102-4fdd-8e9d-009f8b551ce5","translations":[{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"hy","lang_name":"Armenian"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"hi","lang_name":"Hindi"},{"language":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"language":"lo","lang_name":"Lao"},{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"tet","lang_name":"Tetum"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"}]},{"phelps":"BH00009GRA","text":"Ik bün düssen Morgen upstahn dankens Dien Gnaad', o mien Gott, un bün vun mien Tohuus' weggahn mit Vertruen to Di un Œvergaav' an Dien Sorg. Send denn to mi ut d'n Häven vun Dien Gnaad' 'n Sägen vun Dien Sied, un laat mi wedder in Säkerheit trüggkamen, liek as Du mi ünner Dien Schuul weggahn löötst mit mien Sinn stävig an Di. Dat gifft keen annern Gott sünner Di, d'n Enen, d'n Unverglieklichen, d'n Allwätenen, d'n Allwiesen.","name":"Morgengebääd 2","source":"bahaiprayers.org","version":"83e5d83b-8a7d-43cc-a5db-75eebd0db3e5","notes":"Source page has encoding issues with some umlauts; text reconstructed","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bi","lang_name":"Bislama"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ca","lang_name":"Catalan"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"ny","lang_name":"Chichewa"},{"language":"da","lang_name":"Danish"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"et","lang_name":"Estonian"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"},{"language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"haw","lang_name":"Hawaiian"},{"language":"hz","lang_name":"Herero"},{"language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"language":"lb","lang_name":"Luxembourgish"},{"language":"mg","lang_name":"Malagasy"},{"language":"ms","lang_name":"Malay"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"mt","lang_name":"Maltese"},{"language":"mh","lang_name":"Marshallese"},{"language":"mn","lang_name":"Mongolian"},{"language":"ne","lang_name":"Nepali"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"pap","lang_name":"Papiamento"},{"language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"sl","lang_name":"Slovenian"},{"language":"st","lang_name":"Southern Sotho"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"language":"uk","lang_name":"Ukrainian"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"}]},{"phelps":"BH00009SHE","text":"In Dien Schuul bün upwaakt, o mien Gott, un dat is recht, dat de, de düsse Schuul sökt, in dat Hilligdoom vun Dien Bistand un in de Borg vun Dien Wehr verwielen deit. Maak mien Binnerst hell, o mien Herr, mit de Herrlichkeit vun de Ucht vun Dien Apenbaren, so as Du mien Büterst mit dat Morgenlicht vun Dien Pracht hell maakt hest.","name":"Morgengebääd 1","source":"bahaiprayers.org","version":"27388d87-740c-4c67-b260-a7fdf480097c","notes":"Source page has encoding issues with some umlauts; text reconstructed","translations":[{"language":"af","lang_name":"Afrikaans"},{"language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"language":"ar-translit","lang_name":"Arabic (Latin)"},{"language":"az","lang_name":"Azerbaijani"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"sne","lang_name":"Bau Bidayuh"},{"language":"be","lang_name":"Belarusian"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Ben